# Module Map

Last refreshed: 2026-03-08 (Phase 5 - Finalize Docs and Summary).

| Module | Path | Responsibility | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Backend Core Config | `Huz-Backend/huz` | Django settings, root URL routing, ASGI/WSGI bootstrapping | Root URL includes `/api/v1`, `/common`, `/partner`, `/bookings`, `/management`, `/chat` |
| Common Domain | `Huz-Backend/common` | End-user auth/profile, OTP, address, firebase token, user wallet/account primitives | 17 backend endpoints; 10 currently consumed by FE |
| Partner Domain | `Huz-Backend/partners` | Partner auth/profile, package lifecycle, website listing APIs, partner wallet ops | 37 backend endpoints; 36 consumed by FE |
| Booking Domain | `Huz-Backend/booking` | Booking creation/payment/passport, partner booking operations, complaints/reviews/requests | 34 legacy booking endpoints; 31 consumed by FE |
| Booking v1 API | `Huz-Backend/booking/api_urls.py`, `Huz-Backend/booking/views/api_v1.py` | DRF booking endpoints under `/api/v1` | 5 v1 endpoints; 3 consumed by FE |
| Management Domain | `Huz-Backend/management` | Super-admin approvals, payment transfer, reporting/KPI, hotel master catalog | 24 endpoints; 9 consumed by FE |
| Chat Domain | `Huz-Backend/chat` | REST chat inbox/message endpoints + websocket routing | 5 REST endpoints; 0 consumed by current FE API literals |
| Web App Shell | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src` | Public site, booking flow, user settings UI | Routing in `src/routes/AppRoutes.jsx`; current route tree exposes 43 routes (`28` public/auth, `15` protected or alias routes) |
| Web Shared Layout System | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/shared/layout`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/HomePage/homepageLayout.js`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/styles/globals.css` | Shared shell, width/rhythm tokens, branded surfaces, ambient background contract | Primary page-system contract for the revamp; used by Home, Listing, Package Detail, Hajj Guidance, Booking, Payment Methods, Personal Details, and AuthLayout |
| Web Static Content System | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/features/staticPages`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/features/staticPages/content` | Shared branded content shell plus route-driven content modules for public info/legal pages | Powers `HowWeWork`, `AboutUs`, `CoreValues`, `ComingSoon`, `FrequentlyAskedQuestions`, `PolicyPages`, `GenericPages`, `PrivacyPolicy`, and `TermsServices`; Phase 4 verification revalidated the route-driven content coverage for `/refund-policy`, `/cancellation-policy`, `/Media`, and `/career`; remaining manual-wrapper marketing pages are now outside this system |
| Web Auth Surface | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/features/auth`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/Login`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/Signup`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/Otp` | OTP-driven traveler signup/login/verification flow | All auth routes now funnel through `AuthLayout` |
| Web Protected Flow Features | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/features/booking`, `paymentMethods`, `travelersInfo`, `remainingPayment`, `bookingStatus` | Shared hooks/components for protected booking and account flows | Core state ownership is centralized, but several route owners still branch desktop/mobile layouts inside the route file |
| Web API Layer | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/api` | Website auth/listing/booking API clients | Highest endpoint density in `apiService.js` |
| Web Context and Guard Layer | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/context`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/components/ProtectedRoute` | App-level auth, currency, booking state, and guarded navigation | `App.js` wraps all routes in `AuthContextProvider`, `CurrencyProvider`, and `BookingProvider` |
